{"tid":557191,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲失業男留遺書 友愛邨燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-02-11T06:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T06:59:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb823369b6c84e47023e74757a7ad2aec59be8b1","tid":557191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180211/20302324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F20302324&d=nDiTdU8cgH%2FcSBu6VtOslYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4a53e5de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F20302324&h=6723fc6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180211/20302324</a><br />\n<br />\n25歲失業男留遺書<br />\n友愛邨燒炭亡<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門友愛邨愛明樓一單位，昨晨6時許，一名25歲青年被母親發現，在房間內燒炭自殺，昏迷床上，連忙報警。救護員到場經檢驗，證實事主已經死亡。死者姓鍾，從事運輸工作，惟近1個月失業。警方現場撿獲遺書，初步調查他有金錢問題，事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"166f4dcc009ee505d4085f64d24bf8afe6ea7f65","tid":557191,"uid":124585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb823369b6c84e47023e74757a7ad2aec59be8b1","tid":557191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180211/20302324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F20302324&d=nDiTdU8cgH%2FcSBu6VtOslYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4a53e5de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F20302324&h=6723fc6f\" ta